Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:30.09,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, whenever we are sent into the Crimson Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.74,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,...let's gather together at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:32.60,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:32.60,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.28,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Also, that girl that I said I'd introduce to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.60,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,...still doesn't feel up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.83,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? She doesn't want to meet us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:42.55,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I think that we'd be more composed if we were together, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.16,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has personal issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.70,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.06,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.15,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.93,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kusakabe-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.23,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Satsuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.36,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.86,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to discuss with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:04.39,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well then, come to my classroom at lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.15,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:09.33,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean by "something to discuss", Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.18,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.23,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, class is gonna start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.11,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.81,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,The person who woke up the demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.42,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,... is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:34.56,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.26,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,... was it? {i havent watched the previous eps so dunno if this is "was" or "is"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.65,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,So then "you" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.76,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:46.70,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.66,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,...it's my fault that Yuka and everyone else have been dragged into the Crimson Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.99,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,All because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the next problem... Satsuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.18,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun... Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.28,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:02.76,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.73,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of class, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be daydreaming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.35,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.75,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.81,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.17,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been doing {\i1}something{\i0} staying up late, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.26,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.86,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.16,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Hitting people with textbooks means failing this grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:24.84,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, please throw this noisy piece of trash away quickly. {changed "teacher" to "sensei" but is that your guys's style? lemme know}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.57,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean! What do you mean by "trash"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can play around more during recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.30,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.29,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.83,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to awaken them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:54.90,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Powers that are supposedly dormant inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:57.42,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.39,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me how to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:02.41,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,If these dormant powers are meant for fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.48,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,... then they might awaken if I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.68,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,No, they should awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.58,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:14.01,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your feeling to protect Yuka Minase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:16.84,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,However, haste tends to bring about mistakes. { Quick TL recheck on this line please, the later part of it was untimed so not sure if some meaning is missing }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:20.10,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You can't become an expert overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.13,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.39,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.84,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's something I must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.08,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.09,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Kusakabe-senpai. {changed m to n to match the style earlier but again is it your style to americanize it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.42,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me how to use a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.81,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.27,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.92,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's eat over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.28,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.65,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you, Yuka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.45,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yukiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.12,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.99,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,May I have just a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.83,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Avocado and shrimp, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.63,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,This is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.40,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy, yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.31,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.64,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You said just a bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.21,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.46,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,It was so tasty that I just ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.65,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.37,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:32.70,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this where you get mad at me for eating it all...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.58,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Could it be that you've poisoned it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.70,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.56,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt better after seeing your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.42,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.06,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So {\i1}that's{\i0} what you were going on about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.79,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll smile some more for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:59.74,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. There's no point in reading this bogus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:29.02,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Is he an acquaintance of yours, Yukiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.71,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Uh... kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.09,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.85,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,... someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.00,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.81,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:43.16,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what are you saying, Yuka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.14,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,So that's not it... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.19,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,That person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.47,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to put this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.82,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,He's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.74,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,That person is... also suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.28,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:11.89,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka-san, I didn't think so before but you actually have some pretty nice breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.63,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,They feel so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.98,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on, Yukiko-chan-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.03,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,It's so calming~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a cheery and cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got something to say, then say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping silent and having regrets isn't good for your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just lack the finesse. {TLC}
