Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.68,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,That is a complete set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.93,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the fifth book beside the first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.68,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ Is dat sum To Aru Majutsu no Index in my 11eyes? }
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:07.45,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,The numbers are not just for display, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.44,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Please fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.09,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.54,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-chan has become the librarian,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:16.49,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,so Tadashi said he'd help out and this is how things ended up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.45,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.32,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:21.75,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:25.63,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, let's move that whole set down one shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.75,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Please do it swiftly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.00,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.41,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tadashi, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.62,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.60,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.41,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu Kusakabe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:12.72,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The Kusakabe household has always protected the country and people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.59,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,fulfilling its role as an Onmyouji clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:19.55,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've never questioned becoming an Onmyouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:23.05,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, if I were to become one, I wished to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:32.50,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's a red seal. {sounds correct but TLC jic}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:33.23,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A red seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:38.64,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I hold all five treasured swords of the Kusakabe lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:42.16,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,These demon swords are quite powerful, so I usually have them sealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.33,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,but when the need arises, I summon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.00,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Kogarasu Maru Amakuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.00,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The "Kogarasu Maru" is a double bladed sword similar to both the Chinese straight sword and Japanese {\i1}tachi{\i0}, created by Amakuni, a legendary blacksmith considered the father of the Japanese {\i1}katana.{\i0}{double-edged? no audio for these so idk if right}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.59,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Kashagiri Hiromitsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.59,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This sword was rumored to have cut a {\i1}kasha{\i0} (burning wagon) a demon used to steal dead bodies in half. {lol wtf ResearCheck plz}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.30,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Kannagiri Nagamitsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.30,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This sword was rumored to have cut a demon in disguise as a carpenter in half along with the {\i1}kanna{\i0} (carpenter's plane) it was carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.26,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Dousetsu Raikiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.26,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tachibana Dousetsu is a samurai rumored to have sliced a lightning bolt in half with his sword, {\i1}Raikiri{\i0}, the "lightning blade."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.36,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,and finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.05,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Doujigiri Yatsuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.05,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This sword was rumored to have cut off the head of the demon Shuten Douji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:10.12,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The Kusakabe house, being an Onmyouji clan, was required to have powerful heirs obtain the treasured swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:16.85,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,so it had members of the bloodline fight with real swords, and gave one katana to each victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.34,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,For there to be all five katanas here... {can katana be pluralized? i dunno, it's like saying "sushis"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.11,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,So you won all of them, right? Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:26.22,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, in order to prevent the concentration of all the power at one point,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:29.12,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,there's an unspoken agreement that one person should only get one sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:33.11,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Since they were all legitimate fights, though, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:37.09,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,So because of that, I had to leave my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.44,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.00,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Then this house is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.72,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's my mother's villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:44.83,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Because my life is being sought after by everyone in the main family,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.51,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I moved away from my family and have lived here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.67,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,They are after your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.68,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:54.31,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You got your katanas through legitimate fights, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.01,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe is a distinguished family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.68,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,As a distinguished family, honor is of utmost importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:02.71,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,For someone young, and also a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:07.57,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,to take all of the treasured swords isn't entertaining to my senpais. {"senpais" :/}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:11.31,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, in my last battle, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.71,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep my story at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:22.13,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.24,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.97,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavier than you thought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:55.78,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.91,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:58.82,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.06,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:06.71,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:17.30,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:21.35,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You and Kakeru Satsuki were both raised in an institution, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:21.89,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.04,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:25.71,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:28.35,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see a black moon at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.10,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.61,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,How is Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.52,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,He has no talent with the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:39.10,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Still... it's better than him doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.82,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Will Kakeru-kun's power awaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.14,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,If he's lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:46.66,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,...is my answer for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.42,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Your last match...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.81,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You started talking about it, then stopped halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:01.89,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:07.46,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped talking because you didn't want to talk about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.85,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.35,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I cut down my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:16.97,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,In the fight for the last treasured sword, Doujigiri Yasutsuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:20.24,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I cut down Toushi Kusakabe, my father, the head of the Kusakabe household.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:26.20,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was an official match, the other disciples will probably never forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.16,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.06,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I was on bad terms with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:36.06,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,My father didn't like the fact that I looked up to a certain person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.38,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,A certain person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.40,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Misao Kusakabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.28,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The woman known as the greatest female Onmyouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:47.03,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,However, she broke a law and was banished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.56,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What did she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.83,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,She became a Gehou user.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.48,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Gehou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:15:00.13,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's a method that strays from the Kusakabe ways, which has cult spells and even western magic blended in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:15:04.24,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The real-life definition of Gehou (外法, げほう) is any religion that strays from Buddhism, as opposed to Naihou (内法, ないほう).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.65,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.24,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,This is also a form of Gehou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.41,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Misao-san right now is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.28,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,She was banished seventy years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.69,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,That means she's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.13,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:14.62,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.17,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.83,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.30,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.50,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? By over there, do you mean the Crimson Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:27.47,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.68,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.33,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to keep trying until you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.11,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.77,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.49,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me how to do it with real combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:43.31,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.26,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.78,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me even if it's too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:47.49,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.53,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.91,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm doing this, it's going to happen again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.86,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.41,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the eye will probably not awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your priority on the disposal of the "fragments".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall have to go back to your slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventy years... no... It may be one hundred years this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entrapped witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.48,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,No... please let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you could experience death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.63,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You-!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.46,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.67,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.78,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so conceited after defeating just a single underling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:08.86,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.21,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A black knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice stance-yono. {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one will definitely not awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you protect that guy, he'll only drag you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die early?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.87,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intentions of dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more pitiful than us, who have thrown away our human forms... oh, {\i1}how{\i0} entertaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.42,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Human forms?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:51.41,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying that you were once human?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.84,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,And if we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.45,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You "fragments" have no right to know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:00.48,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:01.37,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.57,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight them blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:06.34,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to protect Yuka Minase, then you must run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.01,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.62,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.91,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Run and live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:25.85,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.12,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.07,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.33,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.17,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've hidden themselves, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.11,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:55.47,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.87,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:05.50,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.62,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.54,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.94,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll distract him. While I do that, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:18.78,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get killed! It's impossible for you, Kakeru-kun! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you as you are! {TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you try, it'll be the same result!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You "fragments" can just disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:32.67,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You've saved me, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gula... he underestimated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it was that Onmyouji woman who killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kukuri...nee...san...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:05.93,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.18,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:10.25,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see... We've returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:14.39,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.92,0:24:16.99,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:21.81,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:23.30,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:25.84,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:27.43,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing is that you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.17,0:24:32.03,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki-kun, Yuka-kun, let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.03,0:24:33.06,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,She's our new ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.07,0:24:47.78,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.78,0:24:49.71,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,The Mask of a Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.95,0:24:53.13,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Could there be an end to this nightmare?
